title: [Classic] Beyond The Denver Dynasty (1987)
description:
Beyond the Denver Dynasty (1987)


Buffy Davis, Elle Rio, Ona Z, Rachel Ryan, Sheena Horne, Tammy Reynolds 


Producer Blake Harrison has a horny lifestyle that's wilder than any of the antics on his TV soap opera. It's truly Beyond the Denver Dynasty...and anything else, for that matter! The carnal couplings are nonstop! Is amorous Amanda (Sheena Horne) up to no good after she and Blake make passionate love? What about Crystal (Penny Morgan)? Will her sex antics with Tom Byron destroy her marriage? Can nasty nympho Alexa (Ona Zee) and that insatiable Brazilian bombshell Elle Rio is in cahoots? And what about Buffy Davis? She came into Blake's life once. Now will she come again, and again? All these passion-probing questions will be answered...but you'll need a scorecard to keep track!!!
